">In Extremis</a></i></li>\n<li><i><a href=\"/wiki/Never_So_Good\" title=\"Never So Good\">Never So Good</a></i></li>\n<li><i><a href=\"/wiki/Anne_Boleyn_(play)\" title=\"Anne Boleyn (play)\">Anne Boleyn</a></i></li>\n<li><i><a href=\"/wiki/55_Days\" title=\"55 Days\">55 Days</a></i></li>\n<li><i><a href=\"/wiki/Drawing_the_Line_(play)\" title=\"Drawing the Line (play)\">Drawing the Line</a></i></li>\n<li><i><a href=\"/wiki/Doctor_Scroggy%27s_War\" title=\"Doctor Scroggy&#39;s War\">Doctor Scroggy's War</a></i></li>\n<li><i><a href=\"/wiki/Lawrence_After_Arabia\" title=\"Lawrence After Arabia\">Lawrence After Arabia</a></i></li></ul>\n</div></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\" class=\"navbox-group\" style=\"width:1%\">With David Hare</th><td class=\"navbox-list navbox-even hlist\" style=\"text-align:left;border-left-width:2px;border-left-style:solid;width:100%;padding:0px\"><div style=\"padding:0em 0.25em\">\n<ul><li><i><a href=\"/wiki/Pravda_(play)\" title=\"Pravda (play)\">Pravda</a></i></li></ul>\n</div></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\" class=\"navbox-group\" style=\"width:1%\">Television</th><td class=\"navbox-list navbox-odd hlist\" style=\"text-align:left;border-left-width:2px;border-left-style:solid;width:100%;padding:0px\"><div style=\"padding:0em 0.25em\">\n<ul><li><i><a href=\"/wiki/Dead_Head_(TV_series)\" title=\"Dead Head (TV series)\">Dead Head</a></i></li>\n<li><i><a href=\"/wiki/Spooks_(TV_series)\" title=\"Spooks (TV series)\">Spooks</a></i></li></ul>\n</div></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\" class=\"navbox-group\" style=\"width:1%\">See also</th><td class=\"navbox-list navbox-even hlist\" style=\"text-align:left;border-left-width:2px;border-left-style:solid;width:100%;padding:0px\"><div style=\"padding:0em 0.25em\">\n<ul><li><a href=\"/wiki/Portable_Theatre_Company\" title=\"Portable Theatre Company\">Portable Theatre Company</a></li></ul>\n</div></td></tr></tbody></table></div>\n<div role=\"navigation\" class=\"navbox\" aria-labelledby=\"John_Whiting_Award\" style=\"padding:3px\"><table class=\"nowraplinks hlist collapsible autocollapse navbox-inner\" style=\"border-spacing:0;background:transparent;color:inherit\"><tbody><tr><th scope=\"col\" class=\"navbox-title\" colspan=\"2\" style=\"background: #CFB53B\"><div class=\"plainlinks hlist navbar mini\"><ul><li class=\"nv-view\"><a href=\"/wiki/Template:John_Whiting_Award\" title=\"Template:John Whiting Award\"><abbr title=\"View this template\" style=\"background: #CFB53B;;background:none transparent;border:none;-moz-box-shadow:none;-webkit-box-shadow:none;box-shadow:none; padding:0;\">v</abbr></a></li><li class=\"nv-talk\"><a href=\"/wiki/Template_talk:John_Whiting_Award\" title=\"Template talk:John Whiting Award\"><abbr title=\"Discuss this template\" style=\"background: #CFB53B;;background:none transparent;border:none;-moz-box-shadow:none;-webkit-box-shadow:none;box-shadow:none; padding:0;\">t</abbr></a></li><li class=\"nv-edit\"><a class=\"external text\" href=\"//en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Template:John_Whiting_Award&amp;action=edit\"><abbr title=\"Edit this template\" style=\"background: #CFB53B;;background:none transparent;border:none;-moz-box-shadow:none;-webkit-box-shadow:none;box-shadow:none; padding:0;\">e</abbr></a></li></ul></div><div id=\"John_Whiting_Award\" style=\"font-size:114%;margin:0 4em\"><a href=\"/wiki/John_Whiting_Award\" title=\"John Whiting Award\">John Whiting Award</a></div></th></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\" class=\"navbox-group\" style=\"background: #CFB53B;width:1%;background: #F0DC82\">1967\u20131969</th><td class=\"navbox-list navbox-odd\" style=\"text-align:left;border-left-width:2px;border-left-style:solid;width:100%;padding:0px\"><div style=\"padding:0em 0.25em\">\n<ul><li><a href=\"/wiki/Tom_Stoppard\" title=\"Tom Stoppard\">Tom Stoppard</a> for <i><a href=\"/wiki/Rosencrantz_and_Guildenstern_Are_Dead\" title=\"Rosencrantz and Guildenstern Are Dead\">Rosencrantz and Guildenstern Are Dead</a></i> and <a href=\"/wiki/Wole_Soyinka\